stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> TollEvent: Vehicle uses facility

    TollEvent --> TagLookup: Away agency reads tag/plate

    TagLookup --> ChargeCreated: Tag found in TVL
    TagLookup --> PayByPlate: No tag match

    PayByPlate --> ChargeCreated: Plate lookup succeeds

    ChargeCreated --> Submitted: Written to ledger\n(private collection)

    Submitted --> Acknowledged: Home agency confirms receipt\n(return code 00)
    Submitted --> Rejected: Validation failure\n(return code 01-13)

    Rejected --> [*]

    Acknowledged --> Posted: Home agency posts\nto customer account
    Acknowledged --> NotPosted: Cannot post\n(disposition D/I/N/S/T/C/O)

    Posted --> Reconciled: Home agency writes\nReconciliation record\n(disposition P)

    NotPosted --> Reconciled: Home agency writes\nReconciliation record\n(with rejection reason)

    Reconciled --> CorrectionNeeded: Either agency\nsubmits correction
    Reconciled --> Settled: Included in\nsettlement period

    CorrectionNeeded --> Submitted: Corrected charge\nresubmitted

    Settled --> Paid: Off-chain payment\nstatus updated

    Paid --> [*]
